>I realize that the two strings I am comparing are different, but

Shane,
It is not able to print the Whole String that is why it is giving you the
(...)
I had the same problem previously. So i created a method boolean
compareString(s1, s2);
which compares the lenght of the string and uses the equals method of the
string. also on error prints out both the string so you can take a look and
find out what the error is. and you can assertTrue(compareString(s1,s2))
I hope this might help.

Amit
